{
  "name": "getBeleg",
  "description": "Retrieves a particular `Beleg` from the \"Datenerfassungsprotokoll\".",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "registrierkasseUuid": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "The `_uuid` of the `Registrierkasse` that contains the requested `Beleg`."
      },
      "belegUuid": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "The `_uuid` of the `Beleg` to fetch."
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "registrierkasseUuid",
      "belegUuid"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "/api/v1/registrierkassen/{registrierkasseUuid}/belege/{belegUuid}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**Beleg-Codes**",
            "**Beleg-Typen**",
            [
              "**Belegdaten**: The complete `Beleg` that has been signed by the \"Signaturerstellungseinheit\" and stored in the \"Datenerfassungsprotokoll\".",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**Beleg-Datum-Uhrzeit**",
                  "**Belegnummer**",
                  "**Betrag-Brutto**",
                  "**Betrag-Netto**",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Besonders-Brutto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Besonders-Netto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Ermaessigt-1-Brutto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Ermaessigt-1-Netto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Ermaessigt-2-Brutto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Ermaessigt-2-Netto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Normal-Brutto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Normal-Netto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Null-Brutto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Betrag-Satz-Null-Netto**: The total amount in cents",
                  "**Externer-Beleg-Belegkreis**",
                  "**Externer-Beleg-Bezeichnung**",
                  "**Externer-Beleg-Referenz**",
                  "**Kassen-ID**",
                  "**Kunde**",
                  "**Notizen**",
                  "**Posten**",
                  "**Rabatte**",
                  "**Storno**: Storno?",
                  "**Storno-Beleg-UUID**: The `Beleg-UUID` property of the `Beleg` to be cancelled",
                  "**Storno-Text**",
                  "**Training**: Training?",
                  "**Unternehmen-Adresse1**",
                  "**Unternehmen-Adresse2**",
                  "**Unternehmen-Fusszeile**",
                  "**Unternehmen-ID**",
                  "**Unternehmen-ID-Typ**",
                  "**Unternehmen-Kopfzeile**",
                  "**Unternehmen-Name**",
                  "**Unternehmen-Ort**",
                  "**Unternehmen-PLZ**",
                  "**Zahlungen**",
                  "**Zertifikat-Seriennummer**"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**JWS**: The signed `Beleg` as a JWS signature token.",
            "**QR**: The portion of the `JWS` token to be used for generating QR codes.",
            "**QR-Link**: A hyperlink that retrieves the `QR` data.",
            "**Registrierkasse-UUID**: The `_uuid` of the `Registrierkasse` that has issued this `Beleg`.",
            "**Signaturerstellungseinheit-UUID**: The `_uuid` of the `Signaturerstellungseinheit` that has signed this `Beleg`.",
            "**_href**: URL of the particular `Beleg` instance.",
            "**_uuid**: Unique ID of the particular `Beleg` instance."
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
